{"tid":985068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港澳門料理　澳門人：澳門十分一都冇","createTime":"2019-01-17T09:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T09:17:43.000Z","uid":47714,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4b7ce2ee60fb8ebbebad7200cafa91aaafd9535b","tid":985068,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155570816162357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155570816162357&d=qZhFGhulo22gTZB6MhwXgleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=147e5507\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155570816162357</a><br />\n<br />\nKevin Ho<br />\n<br />\n如果香港俾葡國統治幾百年，大概我哋依家係食緊馬介休，摩囉雞飯，乾炒免治牛肉飯，薯蓉湯，杏仁批，炸青豆(傳到日本變天婦羅)。<br />\n<br />\n就連廣東麵都會變成落咖哩醬，好似澳門咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/walkedbysio/photos/1569565486658599/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwalkedbysio%2Fphotos%2F1569565486658599%2F&d=qZhFGhulo22gTZB6MhwXgleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=8ce9b5cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/walkedbysio/photos/1569565486658599/</a><br />\n<br />\n// 澳門真正特產 //<br />\n<br />\n我一直認為，真正能夠表現澳門地道風味的手信食物，並不是葡撻杏仁餅豬扒包，而是在每個澳門人心目中都有一定地位的「葡國老人牌」沙甸魚。<br />\n<br />\n這款陪伴了我們好幾十年頭的罐頭，我們稱為「辣魚」，因為其實這個牌子有好幾款味道，但我們永遠偏愛吃紅色罐的辣味。<br />\n<br />\n雖然澳門的葡國人、中國人又或中葡混血（我們稱為土生）偶有走進葡國餐廳，但影響力遠遠不及無所不在的「辣魚」。因為每家茶餐廳都有「辣魚」餐單，包括「辣魚公」(公仔麵) 「辣魚芝士多」(多士) 「辣魚菠蘿包」(港式奶油包) 等等，有時候甚至配有咖哩又或其他味道。而且每個家庭都會存有幾罐「辣魚」作為鎮廚之寶，方便隨時添餸。<br />\n<br />\n幾百年來，葡國人跟中國人表面似是互不干涉，但其實，我們生活上許多大小事的確互有感染。「辣魚」吃法演變也就是澳門殖民特色的其一小小憑證，坊間早已共融的思想行為當然也不算少。<br />\n<br />\n所以我說，「辣魚」及其系列餐單，才是澳門的真正特產，澳門的獨有風味。下次哪國親友到來，都一定要帶他試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/o3njtZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fo3njtZ&h=e4bb096f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChi Kei Lok 以前嘅葡國辣魚正好多，夾豬仔包超正！<br />\n<br />\n劉健城 每次過澳門探朋友 , 佢老母都會比幾罐我<br />\n<br />\nJessie Lei 宿舍有成櫃<br />\n<br />\nFelix Tam 煮出前一丁必備<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉樂 10幾蚊~澳門軟實力!!<br />\n<br />\n海闊天空 重點是每個人都吃~!!<br />\n<br />\nPenelope Puian Ng 每次番台灣必帶物品之一"},{"pid":"b5555144a56c796e863e469caf29917361ef369b","tid":985068,"uid":35094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4913a2939476a6961eebb99e73f0e586301a1dc","tid":985068,"uid":78791,"like":5,"dislike":47,"score":-42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35b11c10bb3bad93575e8b9d2528de0c81fbd814","tid":985068,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"澳門D粉麵真心痴撚線<br />\n正正經經既雲吞麵都加PAT咖喱"},{"pid":"1babcadfe0bdfef96ad5b74123ea03feeb2b9fc0","tid":985068,"uid":50060,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"無視TOPIC <br />\n即將變成港澳罵戰<br />\n<br />\n玄學大師詹惟中, azgyz選手 請準備"},{"pid":"61c84d013436a44867c239e1b72503ed016a6acd","tid":985068,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ecshare.easytonetech.com/Storage/master/product/images/2cd7604177dc42dea25746bdee916463.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fecshare.easytonetech.com%2FStorage%2Fmaster%2Fproduct%2Fimages%2F2cd7604177dc42dea25746bdee916463.jpg&h=20aa0e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMADE IN MACAO馬拉盞"},{"pid":"f82e14d079eaee36aa51cb9b1881091cd21be853","tid":985068,"uid":225295,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"Post上大陸論壇啦"},{"pid":"a5c6f60d78cca1d5c069d11ea3679da2a1cd81b2","tid":985068,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f82e14d079eaee36aa51cb9b1881091cd21be853","tid":985068,"uid":225295,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"Post上大陸論壇啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T