":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"挽你老母臭西"},{"pid":"2af017bcc6642d96a0aed8b9aec1788a88f2ceab","tid":985068,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4913a2939476a6961eebb99e73f0e586301a1dc","tid":985068,"uid":78791,"like":5,"dislike":47,"score":-42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"直線話比人知自己係個窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3231eb51020ff471c833a3b9c0e4ec4ac24eaf3","tid":985068,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/macaohongkong/photos/a.1826647857569561/1852843481616665/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmacaohongkong%2Fphotos%2Fa.1826647857569561%2F1852843481616665%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=qZhFGhulo22gTZB6MhwXgleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=bf0cccd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/macaohongkong/photos/a.1826647857569561/1852843481616665/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n乾免治牛肉飯-一種澳門茶餐廳常見嘅食品，由牛肉粒+薯仔粒+洋蔥干炒之後再加上一隻煎蛋組合而成嘅一個飯。其實炒出嚟係幾香口嘅，不過如果係冇汁不歡嘅人就唔太適合啦，因為佢真係要炒得好乾身先至好食。<br />\n<br />\n#乾免治牛肉飯 #干免牛 #這裏沒有紫薯海膽芝士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQU8dsq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQU8dsq.jpg&h=4c29b50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDaniel Palillo 真正土生葡人o既乾免治，係要炒到細細粒好似芝麻咁細，如果大粒到肉粒咁，就只係一般茶記<br />\n<br />\nNg William 絕對香港 冇嘅嘢 食<br />\n<br />\nChilds Chow 正宗讀法：「乾mean嘔飯」<br />\n<br />\n方丈 免牛澳門一般乾濕都有得食<br />\n<br />\nMargaret Fiona Ngai 最鐘意澳門飲凍飲 比支糖水你自己較甜度<br />\n<br />\nKeanu Chung 一直認知免牛係碎牛肉<br />\n<br />\nBilly Au 我曾比人反問「有乾ga咩」？<br />\n<br />\nTensaki Shinkin 冇汁不歡<br />\n<br />\n謝飛賴 我剛到澳門做嘢，冇為意個&ldquo;干&rdquo;字，叫左免治牛，佢又冇理我，到左之後我問佢咩來?<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/td0/1/16/1f602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftd0%2F1%2F16%2F1f602.png&h=5ffc90d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/td0/1/16/1f602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftd0%2F1%2F16%2F1f602.png&h=5ffc90d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/td0/1/16/1f602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftd0%2F1%2F16%2F1f602.png&h=5ffc90d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMira Fenrietta 以前有間餐廳會落葡腸絲，不過已經成為絕響囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJoe Da Fabian 有濕免治牛飯<br />\n<br />\n港澳小不同 係完全唔同嘅食物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20171107121604/http://blog.billyau.com/posts/944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20171107121604%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fblog.billyau.com%2Fposts%2F944&d=qZhFGhulo22gTZB6MhwXgleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=baaa54dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20171107121604/http://blog.billyau.com/posts/944</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4144/4995480912_3d92888a0e_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.static.flickr.com%2F4144%2F4995480912_3d92888a0e_b.jpg&h=bac7f183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.macauzine.net/?action-viewnews-itemid-978-page-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.macauzine.net%2F%3Faction-viewnews-itemid-978-page-3&d=qZhFGhulo22gTZB6MhwXgleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=c93ff575\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.macauzine.net/?action-viewnews-itemid-978-page-3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.macauzine.net/attachments/2016/05/2_201605111300281ab8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.macauzine.net%2Fattachments%2F2016%2F05%2F2_201605111300281ab8X.jpg&h=72c7ff39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e14b